data.description: Welcome to your mountain retreat! Nestled on a serene hillside, this spacious 3-bedroom home offers breathtaking views and tranquility. Featuring a modern kitchen, cozy fireplace, and expansive deck, it's perfect for both quiet evenings in and entertaining guests. With easy access to hiking trails and downtown Hendersonville's charm, this property combines comfort with nature's beauty. Brand new roof and carpet installed! Structural engineer report attached from sellers FHA purchase in 2021. Spectrum Wi-Fi available. Prelisting Home Inspection available for interested buyers, please contact listing agent. Your mountain sanctuary awaits you on Mountain Shadow Lane!
